title: I got update but nothing happened
body: title. Nothing new has happened I cant buy camille and I cant play poro king. login screen is the same.

replies.body: [Rotating Game Modes](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/210354503-Rotating-Game-Modes-FAQ) begin on Fridays, per the guide.  Camille hasn't been released yet, and I don't have any eta on those specifics.  Hope that helps clear things up!
